com.manyangled.gibbous.optim.convex

Class KKTSolution

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.manyangled.gibbous.optim.convex.KKTSolution

  • public class KKTSolution
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds a solution returned from a KKTSolver.

    This class is not exposed to the user, and is important only if you are implementing a custom KKTSolver.
